snippet: After an opening-round 60, Phil Mickelson shot a 65 at the Waste Management Phoenix Open, leading by four strokes at 17 under par.
abstract: Phil Mickelson takes second-round lead at Waste Management Phoenix Open.

headline.seo: At Phoenix Open, Phil Mickelson Nearly Breaks PGA Tour’s 36-Hole Record
